"{\"uid\": \"abc7.com-post-will-la-ready-host-2028-olympics-mayor-bass-15101408\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS (KABC) --In just a few years,Los Angeles will host the Olympicsand with all the excitement comes some logistical concerns.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KABC-TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.445793506888366e-15, \"text\": \"KABC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KABC-TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KABC-TV\"}, {\"begin\": 35, \"end\": 46, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999991210017241, \"rank\": 8.789622245233921e-07, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympicsand\", \"from\": 57, \"to\": 72}, {\"ngram\": \"all the excitement\", \"from\": 78, \"to\": 96}, {\"ngram\": \"some logistical concerns\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Is the city ready for the global spotlight?\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 141}, {\"ngram\": \"the global spotlight\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How will leaders tackle pressing issues, such as homelessness and the city's infrastructure?\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 266, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"leaders\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 190}, {\"ngram\": \"pressing issues\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 213}, {\"ngram\": \"homelessness\", \"from\": 223, \"to\": 235}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's infrastructure\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris and L.A. were concurrently awarded the 2024 and 2028 Olympics back in 2017.\", \"from\": 268, \"to\": 349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 268, \"end\": 273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994806785, \"rank\": 5.192873513251858e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 278, \"end\": 282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999997355644, \"rank\": 1.8506454362194113e-10, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2024 and 2028 Olympics\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"City officials have been paying close attention to Paris' preparations and are now getting a firsthand look at what it will take to pull off a successful global event.\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 401, \"end\": 406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994806785, \"rank\": 5.192873513251858e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"City officials\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"close attention\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 397}, {\"ngram\": \"a firsthand look\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 457}, {\"ngram\": \"a successful global event\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eyewitness News spoke with Mayor Karen Bass about the massive undertaking for 2028.\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karen Bass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eyewitness News\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"the massive undertaking\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bass believes one of the biggest challenges is going to be what she called a \\\"car-free Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 608, \"end\": 612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"score\": 0.9999765423281266, \"rank\": 1.5519103679796768e-05, \"text\": \"Bass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest challenges\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"car-free Olympics\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We need 3,000 buses to come into town, 3,000 buses will not all be electric vehicles because we are going to have to borrow them from many, many cities,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"3,000 buses\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"town\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 745}, {\"ngram\": \"3,000 buses\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"electric vehicles\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 792}, {\"ngram\": \"many, many cities\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So that in and of itself is going to be a logistical nightmare.\\\"\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a logistical nightmare\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So when people hear the phrase \\\"car free,\\\" some may worry.\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"the phrase\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Does that mean peoplecan'tdrive their vehicles?\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1045, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their vehicles\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It does,\\\" said Bass.\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1063, \"end\": 1067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"score\": 0.9999765423281266, \"rank\": 1.5519103679796768e-05, \"text\": \"Bass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It means that if you are going to go to one of the Olympic venues, you are going to take public transportation.\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic venues\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"public transportation\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what it means, and, you know, for our city where we are born with cars, it's going to be difficult.\\\"\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our city\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"cars\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Parisians and visitors are completely comfortable using Paris' Metro system, L.A.'s is not nearly as popular.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1353, \"end\": 1358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994806785, \"rank\": 5.192873513251858e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1374, \"end\": 1378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999997355644, \"rank\": 1.8506454362194113e-10, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1306}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the recent uptick 